<HL>
   Casino Revenue
   In Atlantic City
   Was Flat in July
   ----
   By Mitchell Pacelle
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
08/02/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
